# Tailwind Styling

- Prefer Tailwind utility classes in JSX; add shared classes in `src/index.css` only when reused.
- Use `@layer base` and `@layer components` to define global and reusable styles.
- Reuse existing utility classes (`btn-primary`, `btn-secondary`, `input-field`, `card`) before adding new ones.
- Keep colors consistent with the dark theme palette and existing class names.
